{"version":1,"entries":{"person_5459512_translations":{"at":1773426814499,"data":{"id":5459512,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"แบมแบม นีวิรินทน์ ลิ่มกังวาฬมงคล","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"BamBam Niwirin Limkangwalmongkol is a nonbinary singer and actor from Pattani, Thailand. They got their start in the entertainment industry as a competitor on \"The Voice Thailand Season 3\" (เดอะวอยซ์ไทยแลนด์ ฤดูกาลที่ 3) and studied western music at Srinakharinwirot University.","name":"Niwirin Limkangwalmongkol","primary":false}}]}},"person_552067_translations":{"at":1772865009110,"data":{"id":552067,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hun is a South Korean actor. Kim graduated from Hanyang University, then began his acting career with the Hanyang Repertory Theatre in 1997. Onscreen, he has played leading roles in indie films such as Way to Go, Rose, The Pit and the Pendulum and When Winter Screams.","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"김태훈","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金太勋 （김태훈），韩国男演员，1975年5月26日出生于韩国庆尚道大邱，汉阳大学戏剧影视专业毕业。\n\n参演作品有《孤胆特工》、《如果你是我5》、《求婚大作战》等。 亲哥哥是韩国演员金泰佑。2012年在《善良的男人》中饰演坏人律师，2013年在情景剧《一丝的纯情》中饰演男一号郑雨盛。 2015年，金泰勋确认出演JTBC金土电视剧《亲爱的恩东啊》，饰演崔在浩。 同年，客串出演tvN金土连续剧《请回答1988》，饰演一名医生。 2017年5月，出演MBC月火剧《守望者》，饰演一名检察官。","name":"金太勋","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金太勳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hoon est un acteur sud-coréen. Kim est diplômé de l'Université de Hanyang, puis a commencé sa carrière d'acteur au Hanyang Repertory Theatre en 1997. À l'écran, il a joué des rôles principaux dans des films indépendants tels que Way to Go, Rose, The Pit and the Pendulum et When Winter Screams. Wikipedia","name":"Kim Tae-hoon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金太勳 （김태훈），韓國男演員，1975 年 5 月 26 日出生於韓國慶尚道大邱，漢陽大學戲劇影視專業畢業。\n\n參演作品有《殺手代父》、《如果你是我 5》、《求婚大作戰》等。\n\n親哥哥是韓國演員金泰佑。2012 年在《善良的男人》中飾演壞人律師，2013 年在情景劇《一絲的純情》中飾演男一號鄭雨盛。\n\n2015 年，金泰勳確認出演 JTBC 金土電視劇《親愛的恩東啊》，飾演崔在浩。\n\n同年，客串出演 tvN 金土聯續劇《請回答 1988》，飾演一名醫生。\n\n2017 年 5 月，出演 MBC 月火劇《保衞奇俠》，飾演一名檢察官。","name":"金太勳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hun (coreano: 김태훈) es un actor surcoreano nacido el 26 de mayo de 1975 en Seúl, Corea del Sur. Está representado por la agencia L'July Entertainment.\n\nEstudió Teatro y Cine en la Hanyang University, donde se formó como actor. Comenzó su carrera en 1997 cuando se unió al grupo teatral de su universidad, el Hanyang Repertory Theatre. A partir de ahí desarrolló una trayectoria profesional en cine, teatro y televisión que se extiende hasta la actualidad. A lo largo de los años ha participado en películas independientes y comerciales, así como en series de televisión populares. Entre sus trabajos destacados en cine figuran películas como «Way to Go, Rose» (2006), «The Pit and the Pendulum» (2009) y «When Winter Screams» (2013). En televisión, ha intervenido en producciones como «The Man from Nowhere» (2010), «You're So Pretty» (2011), «The Innocent Man» (2012), «An Ethics Lesson» (2013) o «Pure Love» (2013), entre otras. Además de su trayectoria en cine y televisión, Kim Tae-hun tiene un hermano mayor también actor, Kim Tae-woo.","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ким Тхэ Хун","primary":false}}]}},"person_1817976_translations":{"at":1772865009747,"data":{"id":1817976,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zeynep Buyrac","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zeynep Buyrac","primary":true}}]}},"person_2589726_translations":{"at":1773211331101,"data":{"id":2589726,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朱云儿，1998年9月23日出生，中国内地女演员，就读于北京电影学院。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhu Yun'er","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhu Yun'er","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжу Юнь Эр","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朱雲兒，1998 年 9 月 23 日出生，中國內地女演員，就讀於北京電影學院。","name":"朱雲兒","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1090097_credits":{"at":1773319436281,"data":{"id":1090097,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1576595,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Majd Mastoura","original_name":"Majd Mastoura","popularity":0.4796,"profile_path":"/thTcznNzdzfomVh5OV9TOSUs5ft.jpg","cast_id":3,"character":"Rafik","credit_id":"64bfcd0605822400cd280ab1","order":0},{"adult":false